### Create a new tour (admin only)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/tours
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}

{
  "destination": "Nairobi",
  "description": "A beautiful tour of Nairobi",
  "price": 100.0,
  "tourType": "City Tour",
  "startDate": "2023-12-01T00:00:00.000Z",
  "endDate": "2023-12-05T00:00:00.000Z"
}

### Get all tours
GET http://localhost:5000/api/tours

### Get a tour by ID
GET http://localhost:5000/api/tours/{{TOUR_ID}}

### Update a tour (admin only)
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/tours/{{TOUR_ID}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}

{
  "destination": "Updated Nairobi"
}

### Soft delete a tour (admin only)
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/tours/{{TOUR_ID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}